WEBVTT

00:05:59.484 --> 00:06:05.022
Ndi enyi soro anyi were too, 
gbanwere ma kpawa oke.

00:06:07.316 --> 00:06:08.839
a nukwaram ochi azu.

00:06:09.628 --> 00:06:11.220
A nukwara m ntamu.

00:06:12.186 --> 00:06:14.416
"I nuru n'isi agbakaala ya?"

00:06:15.275 --> 00:06:17.805
"O yi bago ara!"

00:06:17.849 --> 00:06:22.169
Okwu mkpari na nneda anya 
gbasara onodu ya --

00:06:22.193 --> 00:06:26.170
okwu enweghi ike ikwu gbasara onye n'aria
cancer

00:06:26.194 --> 00:06:27.954
ma o bu oria anwunta.

00:06:28.664 --> 00:06:32.343
ufodu oge, e kwute okwu oria isi mgbaka,